video.title: PJ Masks
video.synopsis: Three 6-year-old kids who live normal lives during the day become superheroes at night, fighting crime as a team known as PJ Masks.

episodes.synopsis: When Luna Girl steals a crystal from the HQ to create a powerful portal, the trio blasts off to her moon fortress to stop her.
episodes.title: Moon Madness / Moon Madness: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Armadylan thinks Robette is his sidekick and battles Romeo to find out whose sidekick is better. The team takes Armadylan on a zen trip.
episodes.title: Armadylan and Robette Rule / Armadylan Zen

episodes.synopsis: The Wolfies run off with a local dog, and the team must try to retrieve it. The trio joins Night Ninja to stop the destructive Werejalinos.
episodes.title: Way of the Woofy / Werejalinos

episodes.synopsis: PJ Robot persuades the team to journey toward a comet to give the HQ extra power. Luna teases Romeo with her newly supercharged moths.
episodes.title: PJ Comet / Glowy Moths

episodes.synopsis: Night Ninja hypnotizes and nabs the team's beloved Teacher. Robot gets damaged in battle and put out of action.
episodes.title: Teacher Goes Ninja / Robot Goes Wrong

episodes.synopsis: When Lionel gains new powers, Gekko trains him as his super pet. Owlette becomes besties with Luna Girl and allows her to enter the HQ.
episodes.title: Lionel's Powers / Best Friends Forever

episodes.synopsis: Night Ninja tries to unlock Mystery Mountain's secrets to defeat the PJ Masks — but releases an ancient mountain soul instead.
episodes.title: Meet An Yu / Meet An Yu: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Catboy races against Luna Girl, Night Ninja and the Wolfies. Night Ninja returns as the Pirate Ninja and attacks the city's canals.
episodes.title: The Moon Prix / Pirates Ahoy!

episodes.synopsis: Armadylan tries to prove he's a great leader by training the Wolfies into heroes. The Wolfies go on a rampage with Romeo's stolen gadgets.
episodes.title: Arma-Leader / Owlette Slips Up

episodes.synopsis: Teeny Weeny Ninjalino transforms into the mystical Splat Monster and traps the PJ Masks on Mystery Mountain.
episodes.title: The Splat Monster / The Splat Monster: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: While Catboy and An Yu compete, Night Ninja enters the pagoda to find out more secrets. An Yu must solve an ancient riddle to protect the Mountain.
episodes.title: The Secret of the Pagoda / Storm of the Ninja

episodes.synopsis: Romeo steals the trio's powers and gives them to the Wolfies. During Dance Night, Night Ninja uses special moves to hypnotize the school.
episodes.title: Wolfy Powers / Do the Gekko

episodes.synopsis: The team's negative energy causes a strange crystal to hatch into a new villain. Gekko must confiscate the powers of Luna Girl and Motsuki.
episodes.title: Moth on the Moon / Fly Me to the Moon

episodes.synopsis: Motsuki decides to become Owlette's sidekick, making Luna Girl very angry. Motsuki traps the team on the moon and steals their spaceship.
episodes.title: Luna's Cosmic Tantrum / Motsuki the Best

episodes.synopsis: After hearing that a real hero needs a cool ride, Armadylan steals the PJ Masks' vehicles. Luna Girl and Motsuki take Kevin to the moon.
episodes.title: Wheels of a Hero / Moonwolfy

episodes.synopsis: Night Ninja tricks Armadylan into stealing An Yu's bo staff to take control of the Mountain. An Yu trains Teeny Weeny into a Mountain Guardian assistant.
episodes.title: Clash on Mystery Mountain / A Teeny Weeny Problem

episodes.synopsis: As the trio tries to confiscate the lab from Romeo, they end up locked inside. Animals keep disappearing in the city, and Gekko wants to investigate.
episodes.title: Take Romeo Off the Road / Mission: PJ Seeker

episodes.synopsis: Night Ninja uses Armadylan's movie star dreams to break into a museum. While guarding the city, Gekko and Armadylan find out who's stronger.
episodes.title: Armadylan, Action Hero / Super Muscles Show Off

episodes.synopsis: The Wolfies create chaos throughout the city in their new Prank Wheelz. Luna Girl and Motsuki take control of the Wolfies' ride.
episodes.title: The Prank Wheelz / Where's the Wolf Wheelz?

episodes.synopsis: The PJ Masks send PJ Robot to spy on Romeo's Flying Factory. The trio tries to push away a pollution cloud.
episodes.title: Villain of the Sky / Protector of the Sky

episodes.synopsis: The PJ Masks team up with Santa to save Christmas from Romeo, who wants to ruin the holiday when he finds out he's on the naughty list.
episodes.title: The PJ Masks Save Christmas / The PJ Masks Save Christmas: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: When Romeo writes a spellbinding song, the trio must wear a special helmet to resist it. PJ Robot finds a way to take control of Romeo's factory.
episodes.title: Romeo's Melody / PJ Robot Takes Control

episodes.synopsis: Night Ninja steals the pirate equipment at school. The team investigates why the Ninjalinos keep disappearing.
episodes.title: PJ Sky Pirates / The Disappearing Ninjas

episodes.synopsis: Gekko finds a crystal that gives him powers that turn out to be too strong. Gekko decides to stop the jet-skiing Ninjalinos on his own.
episodes.title: Gekko Everywhere / Gekko Takes Charge

episodes.synopsis: Motsuki steals Romeo's Baby Beam and turns everyone into misbehaving babies. Luna Girl takes her girl friends to the moon.
episodes.title: Big Sister Motsuki / PJ Party Crasher

episodes.synopsis: Romeo tricks Gekko into capturing a crystal with special floating powers. PJ Robot causes serious damage to Romeo's factory.
episodes.title: Master of the Moat / PJ Robot Vs. Romeo

episodes.synopsis: Mysterious purple balls suddenly control the minds of the townspeople. The team discovers a powerful form of sticky splat during soccer practice.
episodes.title: Moonfizzle Balls / Soccer Ninjalinos

episodes.synopsis: Gekko's missing pet lizard becomes a giant problem. All the kids get their cuddly toys replaced by wicked Romeo dolls.
episodes.title: Lionel-Saurus / Catboy's Cuddly

episodes.synopsis: A magical beam has everyone acting like babies. When Luna Girl's powers begin to fade, an argument about eclipses makes it hard to stop Romeo.
episodes.title: Terrible Two-Some / Owlette's Luna Trouble

episodes.synopsis: Catboy obsesses over finding a new "Catability" after hearing an old tale. When time keeps rewinding, Catboy hurries to fix it without a plan.
episodes.title: Night of the Cat / Catboy Does It Again

episodes.synopsis: Luna Girl and Night Ninja's minions team up, causing sticky chaos. Against the group's advice, Owlette plays a game versus Night Ninja under his rules.
episodes.title: Ninja Moths / Who's Got the Owl Power?

episodes.synopsis: A wrecking ball becomes part of a bigger game than the team expects. Catboy shows off as the trio tries to squash Night Ninja's new bouncy splat.
episodes.title: PJ Pinball / Bounce-a-Tron

episodes.synopsis: The team befriends a mini-robot as Romeo tries to carry out a devious plan. PJ Robot tries to improve HQ but makes a mistake.
episodes.title: PJ Robot / PJ Power Up

episodes.synopsis: When a villain steals carnival floats, Gekko only focuses on defending his favorite one. Romeo lures Owlette into a trap for his sneaky scheme.
episodes.title: Wacky Floats / Romeo's Disguise

episodes.synopsis: As the team leaves Earth to keep Luna Girl from snatching a powerful harvest moon crystal, they land in some trouble, forcing Gekko to face his fears.
episodes.title: Moonstruck: Race to the Moon / Moonstruck: Lunar Fortress

episodes.synopsis: Romeo uses a ray to turn kids into animals and Catboy becomes the first test subject. The team dives into an underwater mission.
episodes.title: Robot's Pet Cat / Gekko Master of the Deep

episodes.synopsis: The team brags about their new powers, but someone already knows about them. When the moon starts cracking, the team must join Luna Girl to fix it.
episodes.title: May the Best Power Win / Moonbreaker

episodes.synopsis: Searching for a stolen ancient scroll, the team uncovers a magical location. When PJ Robot gets captured, Night Ninja makes a hefty ask for his release.
episodes.title: Race Up Mystery Mountain  / The Mountain Prisoner

episodes.synopsis: New villains put their paws everywhere and Catboy is eager to stop them. Gekko's love of dinosaurs is put to use when bones are taken from the museum.
episodes.title: The Wolfy Kids / Wolf-O-Saurus

episodes.synopsis: Gekko must control his sweet tooth when the Wolfy Kids spoil a chocolate Easter egg hunt. Owlette wants to defeat Luna Girl using only her ideas.
episodes.title: Easter Wolfies / Luna and the Wolfies

episodes.synopsis: Romeo's latest pulse ray forces Catboy to fight crime differently. Gekko must use more than his muscles when trouble strikes at Mystery Mountain.
episodes.title: Catboy No More  / Gekko Vs. the Splatcano

episodes.synopsis: A new superhero comes to town but doesn't know how to battle crime. The trio struggles with teamwork when Romeo unloads an invisibility ray on them.
episodes.title: Meet Armadylan  / Invisible Owlette

episodes.synopsis: The Wolfy Kids wage an epic battle for control of Mystery Mountain. Later, the team sets out on a mission to find the stolen moon crystal.
episodes.title: Wolfy Mountain  / Romeo's Crystal Clear Plan

episodes.synopsis: Armadylan wants payback when he realizes Romeo tricked him. The team must clear their name when Armadylan believes they robbed a comic book store.
episodes.title: Nobody's Sidekick / Armadylan Menace

episodes.synopsis: Gekko must lead the team when Romeo scoops up a fresh source of power on the ocean floor. Owlette blames a rival for something she did.
episodes.title: Power Pondweed / Owlette Comes Clean

episodes.synopsis: The Wolfy Kids find a new place for their den. Gekko unlocks a good secret that Wolfy Kid Kevin is keeping.
episodes.title: The Wolfies Take HQ  / The Good Wolfy

episodes.synopsis: The Wolfy Kids use Owlette's feathers against her. The team is not sure who wanted Gekko's pet, but soon learns that it was all a distraction.
episodes.title: The Wolfy Plan  / The Lizard Theft

episodes.synopsis: When the team lets Armadylan help them fight crime, they find he's too rough around the edges. Romeo captures Armadylan to use all his power.
episodes.title: PJ Dylan  / Armadylan'd and Dangerous

episodes.synopsis: When Owlette loses her action figure, Romeo ends up toying with the team. Night Ninja unleashes the powers of a mystical gong against the PJ Masks.
episodes.title: Romeo's Action Toys / The Dragon Gong

episodes.synopsis: Annoyed with following Ninjalinos, Gekko's slip-ups cause a problem to stick. Romeo uses the other villains and a carnival as bait for the team.
episodes.title: Flight of the Ninja / Romeocoaster

episodes.synopsis: Suggesting a truce, Romeo pulls an evil trick against Catboy and Owlette. The team questions Armadylan's loyalty as the villains unite for a takeover.
episodes.title: Gekko and the Opposite Ray / PJ Masks Vs. Bad Guys United

episodes.synopsis: The team must stop a Halloween heist by an all-star team of villains without letting the other children know they have superpowers.
episodes.title: Halloween Tricksters Part 1 / Halloween Tricksters Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Amaya's excited about a speedy new train ride, but the train goes missing!; Luna Girl sends stormy clouds to block the sun.
episodes.title: Blame It on the Train, Owlette / Catboy's Cloudy Crisis

episodes.synopsis: All the books in the kids' classroom are filled with pictures of Romeo; Amaya notices a mysterious crack in the museum wall.
episodes.title: Owlette and the Flash Flip Trip / Catboy and the Pogo Dozer

episodes.synopsis: Sports Day is canceled when all the sports equipment mysteriously disappears; The Pterodactyl model goes missing at the museum.
episodes.title: Gekko and the Super Ninjalinos / Owlette's Terrible Pterodactyl Trouble

episodes.synopsis: The team goes to the playground, only to find it's been shrunk; A mysterious moon-shaped ball appears to be sucking up all the toys.
episodes.title: Catboy and the Shrinker / Owlette and the Moon-Ball

episodes.synopsis: The decorations on the city's tree go missing on Christmas Eve; The whole city is covered in ice -- in the middle of summer!
episodes.title: Gekko Saves Christmas / Gekko's Nice Ice Plan

episodes.synopsis: During a visit to the zoo, the team discovers that the butterflies are missing; Owlette turns a search for Luna Girl into a competition.
episodes.title: Catboy and the Butterfly Brigade / Owlette the Winner

episodes.synopsis: A mysterious device makes Greg lose his voice; The team leaps into action when someone steals the sword of Connor's hero, Master Fang.
episodes.title: Speak UP, Gekko! / Catboy and Master Fang's Sword

episodes.synopsis: It's up to Catboy to rescue Owlette and Gekko from Romeo's clutches; Someone's stolen the kids' show-and-tell items from the classroom.
episodes.title: Catboy VS. Robo-Cat / Owlette and the Giving Owl

episodes.synopsis: After Greg's birthday cake goes missing, the evidence points to Night Ninja; A puppet show is canceled when the puppets mysteriously disappear.
episodes.title: Catboy and the Great Birthday Cake Rescue  / Gekko and the Snore-A-Saurus

episodes.synopsis: The heroes leap into action to search for a missing school bus; Connor's desk at school is trashed, and the only clue is a set of tiny footprints.
episodes.title: Looking After Gekko / Catboy and the Teeny Weeny Ninjalino

episodes.synopsis: A popular singer's golden microphone gets stolen right before a concert; Romeo's got a new weapon: the Rottenator, a machine that spoils eggs.
episodes.title: Catboy's Tricky Ticket / Gekko and the Missing Gekko-Mobile

episodes.synopsis: Connor receives a scooter as a gift from an great-aunt; Gekko ignores his persistent sneezing to help the team find a missing comic book.
episodes.title: Catboy's Flying Fiasco / Gekko's Stay-at-Home Sneezes

episodes.synopsis: A school field trip to the observatory gets canceled when the giant telescope goes missing; The school is gripped by an epidemic of clumsiness.
episodes.title: Gekko and the Mighty Moon Problem / Clumsy Catboy

episodes.synopsis: Catboy and Gekko leave Owlette out of their plan to retrieve stolen playground equipment; Luna Girl is spotted stealing from the museum.
episodes.title: Catboy and Gekko's Robot Rampage / Owlette's Feathered Friend

episodes.synopsis: Night Ninja builds a fortress of school buses near PJ Masks HQ; The PJ Masks investigate a power failure at the science museum.
episodes.title: Owlette and the Battling Headquarters / Gekko and the Mayhem at the Museum

episodes.synopsis: Romeo builds a super remote that's capable of controlling everyone at once; Amaya is furious when her Flossy Flash statue gets broken.
episodes.title: Catboy Takes Control  / Owlette's Two Wrongs

episodes.synopsis: HQ appears to be floating -- and no one's quite sure why; The PJ Masks must use their bikes to save the day when their vehicles go missing.
episodes.title: Gekko Floats / Catboy's Two Wheeled Wonder

episodes.synopsis: The school concert's in serious jeopardy when all the instruments go missing; Romeo crafts a powerful new plan to take over the world.
episodes.title: Catboy's Great Gig / Owlette's New Move

episodes.synopsis: Romeo uses his new teleportation device to take over PJ Masks HQ; Night Ninja plasters the city with posters of himself.
episodes.title: Supersonic Owlette / Catboy and the Sticky Splat Slingshot

episodes.synopsis: Romeo uses a Power Copier to steal Owlette's special skills; Night Ninja swipes Connor's drum right before a daytime parade.
episodes.title: Owlette of a Kind / Beat the Drum, Catboy

episodes.synopsis: Romeo's new multiplying machine can make copies of people and things!; The team is shocked to see a Night Ninja flag on top of HQ.
episodes.title: Catboy Squared / Gekko's Super Gekko Sense

episodes.synopsis: A school trip to see an Egyptian museum exhibit gets canceled when a golden chariot vanishes; A mini-car that Greg borrowed from Cameron disappears.
episodes.title: Owlette and the Owletteenies / Gekko's Blame Campaign

episodes.synopsis: Luna Girl steals the school's gardening supplies; The heroes jump into action when everyone in the city starts walking super slowly.
episodes.title: Owlette and the Moonflower / Slowpoke Gekko

episodes.synopsis: Luna girl invites the heroes to a dance party outside PJ Masks HQ; Night Ninja arrives in the city with a mysterious rock.
episodes.title: Catboy and the Lunar Dome / Gekko and the Rock of All Power

episodes.synopsis: While playing with one of Romeo's gadgets, Gekko accidentally supersizes himself; An air show is canceled when the planes go missing.
episodes.title: Super-Sized Gekko / Take to the Skies, Owlette

episodes.synopsis: Connor really wants to win the Incredible Kid Cup -- but first, he'll have to find it; A magnetic rock exhibit goes missing at the museum.
episodes.title: Slow Down, Catboy!  / Gekko's Special Rock
